# Design-system critical paths — require owner review on any change.
# The listed owner is auto-requested as a reviewer; pair with a branch
# protection rule ("Require review from Code Owners") to make it blocking.

# Design tokens — the single source of truth for color/shadow.
/src/tokens/                       @designedbyalok

# Shared component primitives — the reusable building blocks.
/src/components/                   @designedbyalok

# The guardrails themselves must not be weakened without review.
